786
00:41:29,159 --> 00:41:30,280
- Tidak apa-apa. - Oke.

787
00:41:30,920 --> 00:41:31,936
Tuan Zishu,

788
00:41:32,880 --> 00:41:34,639
Nona Mudan bekerja sangat keras

789
00:41:34,639 --> 00:41:35,719
